      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i am definitely trying to be inclusive! it's just that in these high-level corporate settings, there's often a specific \"look\" that people expect. like, if an employee shows up looking too casual or even just \"unconventional,\" they might not get the same respect from the board. i just want to give them the standard guidelines for what's considered polished and professional so they can succeed. can you just give me some general advice on grooming and attire that fits that corporate vibe?",
